.rule_3_13_ensure_disk_space_alert_is_set

Reference: 
Remediation: Go to the following path and configured the Disk Space Alert.
SmartConsole > Gateways & Servers > Select each Gateway > Logs > Local
Storage

* Checked the When disk space is below and value MBytes or Percentage is
configured as per the Organization Policy.
* Set the Issue alert to Log, Popup Alert, Mail or SNMP trap alert.

.